title: Tryn not that much stronger overall
body: But his early game sustain with warlords blood lust and a crit path is pretty good. Usually have a medium priority on a lifesteal item with tryn (after key damage item) but warlords means that is not as important.

replies.body: are you trying to get the mastery nerfed
I see you haven't played him jungle then. Last season Tryndamere would often get extremely low on the first clear. Now he's clearing 3x as fast, and staying very healthy.
I haven't played him jg yet but I can see how that would be very good with the warlords.
